<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/faviconlogo.png" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Howdy English - Coming Soon</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Learn English through podcasts. Coming soon.">
    
    <!-- Google Fonts -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Nunito:wght@700;800&family=Noto+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar">
        <div class="container">
            <a class="logo" href="/"><img src="/howdylogoforsite.png" alt="Howdy English" style="height:40px; width:auto;" /></a>
            <div class="nav-actions">
                <a class="store-btn" href="#">App Store</a>
                <a class="store-btn" href="#">Google Play</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <section class="hero">
        <div class="container hero-grid">
            <div class="hero-copy">
                <p class="hero-label">⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ &nbsp;Loved by English learners worldwide</p>
                <h1 class="hero-title">
                    <span class="hero-title-line">Speak English with</span>
                    <span class="hero-title-line">real confidence.</span>
                </h1>
                <p class="hero-subheadline">Real podcast conversations. Vocabulary you actually use. Speaking practice with feedback that helps you improve.</p>
                <div class="hero-actions">
                    <a class="hero-btn hero-btn-ios" href="#">Download on iOS</a>
                    <a class="hero-btn hero-btn-android" href="#">Get it on Android</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="hero-visual">
                <img
                    class="hero-image"
                    src="/assets/images/hero-woman.png"
                    alt="Learner practicing English with headphones"
                    width="768"
                    height="1024"
                    loading="eager"
                    decoding="async"
                />
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section style="background:#ffffff; padding:80px 24px; text-align:center;">
      <p style="color:#0075F2; font-size:12px; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:2px; text-transform:uppercase; margin-bottom:12px;">HOW IT WORKS</p>
      <h2 style="font-size:32px; font-weight:800; color:#111; margin-bottom:48px;">Three steps to fluency</h2>
      <div style="display:flex; gap:40px; justify-content:center; flex-wrap:wrap; max-width:900px; margin:0 auto;">
        <div style="flex:1; min-width:220px; max-width:280px;">
          <div style="font-size:48px; margin-bottom:16px;">🎧</div>
          <h3 style="font-size:20px; font-weight:700; margin-bottom:8px;">Listen</h3>
          <p style="color:#555; font-size:15px; line-height:1.6;">Follow real podcast conversations between native speakers</p>
        </div>
        <div style="flex:1; min-width:220px; max-width:280px;">
          <div style="font-size:48px; margin-bottom:16px;">📖</div>
          <h3 style="font-size:20px; font-weight:700; margin-bottom:8px;">Learn</h3>
          <p style="color:#555; font-size:15px; line-height:1.6;">Tap words to save them. Quizzes reinforce what you heard</p>
        </div>
        <div style="flex:1; min-width:220px; max-width:280px;">
          <div style="font-size:48px; margin-bottom:16px;">🎤</div>
          <h3 style="font-size:20px; font-weight:700; margin-bottom:8px;">Speak</h3>
          <p style="color:#555; font-size:15px; line-height:1.6;">AI gives you a topic and grades your spoken response</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section style="background:#ffffff; padding:80px 24px; max-width:900px; margin:0 auto;">
      <p style="color:#0075F2; font-size:12px; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:2px; text-transform:uppercase; margin-bottom:12px; text-align:center;">ABOUT</p>
      <h2 style="font-size:32px; font-weight:800; color:#111; margin-bottom:24px; text-align:center;">Built by a teacher, for learners</h2>
      <p style="color:#555; font-size:16px; line-height:1.8; margin-bottom:28px;">I've taught hundreds of adult English learners and watched them struggle with apps that feel like homework. I built Howdy English because I wanted something different — an app that actually works for adults who are serious about getting to the next level. Real conversations. Real feedback. Real progress.</p>
      <p style="color:#555; font-size:16px; line-height:1.7; font-style:italic;">— Jeff, founder of Howdy English &amp; English teacher</p>
    </section>

    <footer style="background:#ffffff; padding:40px 24px; text-align:center;">
      <p style="color:#FF6B35; font-size:18px; font-weight:700; margin-bottom:16px;">Howdy English</p>
      <div style="display:flex; gap:24px; justify-content:center; flex-wrap:wrap; margin-bottom:24px;">
        <a href="/privacy" style="color:#555; font-size:14px; text-decoration:none;">Privacy Policy</a>
        <a href="/terms" style="color:#555; font-size:14px; text-decoration:none;">Terms of Service</a>
        <a href="mailto:support@howdyenglish.app" style="color:#555; font-size:14px; text-decoration:none;">Support</a>
      </div>
      <p style="color:#555; font-size:13px;">© 2026 Howdy English. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>

    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Noto Sans', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            color: #1a1a1a;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        .navbar {
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eeeeee;
        }

        .navbar .container {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            min-height: 72px;
            gap: 16px;
        }

        .logo {
            color: #FF6B35;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 1.2;
        }

        .nav-actions {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
        }

        .store-btn {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            min-height: 40px;
            padding: 0 16px;
            border: 1px solid #d9d9d9;
            border-radius: 999px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            color: #1a1a1a;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            transition: background-color 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
        }

        .store-btn:hover {
            background-color: #f3f3f3;
            border-color: #cfcfcf;
        }

        .hero {
            padding: 64px 24px 80px;
            background: #ffffff;
        }

        .hero-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
            gap: 48px;
            align-items: center;
            max-width: 1200px;
        }

        .hero-copy {
            grid-column: 1;
            min-width: 0;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .hero-visual {
            grid-column: 2;
            min-width: 0;
            justify-self: stretch;
        }

        .hero-label {
            font-family: 'Noto Sans', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #555;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            letter-spacing: 0.01em;
        }

        .hero-title {
            font-family: 'Nunito', 'Noto Sans', sans-serif;
            font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 4vw + 1rem, 3.25rem);
            font-weight: 800;
            line-height: 1.1;
            color: #111;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .hero-title-line {
            display: block;
        }

        .hero-subheadline {
            font-family: 'Noto Sans', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
            font-size: 17px;
            line-height: 1.65;
            color: #555;
            margin-bottom: 28px;
            max-width: 520px;
        }

        .hero-actions {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 12px;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: flex-start;
        }

        .hero-btn {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            min-height: 48px;
            padding: 0 22px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-family: 'Noto Sans', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 15px;
            transition: background-color 0.2s, color 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
        }

        .hero-btn-ios {
            background: #0075F2;
            color: #fff;
            border: 2px solid #0075F2;
        }

        .hero-btn-ios:hover {
            background: #0066d4;
            border-color: #0066d4;
        }

        .hero-btn-android {
            background: transparent;
            color: #0075F2;
            border: 2px solid #0075F2;
        }

        .hero-btn-android:hover {
            background: rgba(0, 117, 242, 0.06);
        }

        .hero-image {
            display: block;
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            max-height: min(520px, 75vh);
            object-fit: contain;
            object-position: center bottom;
            border-radius: 16px;
        }

        .how-it-works {
            background: #ffffff;
            padding: 80px 24px;
        }

        .how-label {
            text-align: center;
            color: #0075F2;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.08em;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .how-title {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #111;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .how-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
            gap: 24px;
        }

        .how-step {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .how-emoji {
            font-size: 40px;
            line-height: 1;
            margin-bottom: 14px;
        }

        .how-step h3 {
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #111;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .how-step p {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #555;
            max-width: 320px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        /* Responsive: stack copy → image; full-bleed image on small screens */
        @media (max-width: 900px) {
            .hero {
                padding: 48px 0 64px;
            }

            .hero-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 32px;
                padding-left: 0;
                padding-right: 0;
            }

            .hero-copy {
                grid-column: 1;
                padding-left: 24px;
                padding-right: 24px;
                text-align: center;
            }

            .hero-subheadline {
                margin-left: auto;
                margin-right: auto;
                max-width: 36rem;
            }

            .hero-actions {
                justify-content: center;
            }

            .hero-visual {
                grid-column: 1;
                width: 100%;
                max-width: none;
                margin: 0;
                justify-self: stretch;
            }

            .hero-image {
                width: 100%;
                max-width: none;
                max-height: none;
                border-radius: 0;
                object-fit: contain;
                object-position: center;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .navbar .container {
                min-height: 64px;
            }

            .how-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 28px;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 560px) {
            .navbar .container {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: flex-start;
                justify-content: center;
                padding-top: 12px;
                padding-bottom: 12px;
            }

            .nav-actions {
                width: 100%;
            }

            .store-btn {
                flex: 1;
                text-align: center;
            }

        }
    </style>
</body>
</html>